'''威廉·蓋瑟·“比利”·克鲁德普'''（{{lang-en|William Gaither "Billy" Crudup}}，{{bd|1968年|7月8日|||catIdx=K }}），美国知名男演员。

==生平==
克鲁德普出生在[[美国|美国]][[纽约州|纽约州]]的{{link-en|曼哈西特|Manhasset, New York}}。克鲁德普的父亲和母亲在他孩童时就离婚了。<ref>{{cite news | author= | title=Billy Crudup Biography | url=http://movies.yahoo.com/shop?d=hc&id=1800019546&cf=biog&intl=us | work=Yahoo! Movies | date= | accessdate=2008-05-21 | archive-date=2007-03-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070310075910/http://movies.yahoo.com/shop?d=hc&id=1800019546&cf=biog&intl=us | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=florid1>{{cite news|last=Evertz|first=Mary|coauthors=|title=Crudup family keeps busy in New York Series: PEOPLE|pages=|publisher=St. Petersburg Times|date=2001-10-26|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/sptimes/access/86137546.html?dids=86137546:86137546&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Oct+26%2C+2001&author=MARY+EVERTZ&pub=St.+Petersburg+Times&desc=Crudup+family+keeps+busy+in+New+York+Series%3A+PEOPLE&pqatl=google|accessdate=2010-05-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=esMyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dusFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3352,313549&dq=our-towns-gaither-cruet-up-storybook-nuptial&hl=en |title=The Miami News - Google News Archive |publisher=News.google.com |date=1966-07-17 |accessdate=2012-06-22 |archive-date=2015-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013235511/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=esMyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dusFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3352,313549&dq=our-towns-gaither-cruet-up-storybook-nuptial&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>

克鲁德普毕业于[[北卡罗来纳大学教堂山分校|北卡罗来纳大学教堂山分校]]、[[纽约大学|纽约大学]]。

==家庭==
1996年，克鲁德普開始和[[玛丽-露易斯·帕克|玛丽-露易斯·帕克]]同居，两人育有一子（William Atticus Parker）；2003年，兩人因克鲁德普和[[克萊兒·丹妮絲|克萊兒·丹妮絲]]一起而分手，但克鲁德普和丹妮絲最後亦於2006年分手收場。

